{"tid":1218623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［反送中撚注意］前港督彭定康先生為香港釋法","createTime":"2019-06-13T16:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:05:42.000Z","uid":222605,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e9a115d04ee620d725a686dc05e268f609e35631","tid":1218623,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"香港前港督彭定康先生<br />\n為我地解讀<br />\n推行逃犯條例對香港帶來的影響<br />\n<br />\n內容講到<br />\n普通法已經能夠處理到逃犯嘅問題<br />\n而且不會為香港、英國、中國之間<br />\n實行引渡條例<br />\n<br />\n因為香港和內地的情況非常不同<br />\n一旦改變<br />\n會造成極大嘅不確定與擔憂<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sD72Jqh0WVA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsD72Jqh0WVA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=bcdac4a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sD72Jqh0WVA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n彭定康先生承認<br />\n在香港推行民主的時間太少<br />\n<br />\n假如香港當時有多5至10年的民主經驗<br />\n中國政府想令香港民主倒退<br />\n會變得更加困難<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/smLGK2c9V0w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsmLGK2c9V0w&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWRV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=a5133d42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/smLGK2c9V0w</a>"},{"pid":"caef005a8082712bdc90a215aba2a0fe9b208fd2","tid":1218623,"uid":222605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"港督先生講嘅野<br />\n真係好有權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25e9df54a29eaa757e72c5c8ae97ef4e98d6429","tid":1218623,"uid":222605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你離開咗香港咁耐<br />\n都仲肯為香港講句公道說話<br />\n真係一個好有責任心嘅港督<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343ffdde41f2e909d89a2f7be7118526ec90d8ca","tid":1218623,"uid":222605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p